introBody:
CodePachinko tries to teach introductory Python topics through a game.

You write code:
- to drop balls;
- to choose where a ball drops from;
- to decide which balls to skip;
- to earn points.

You can spend points on upgrades.

In the game, you go through these topics: 1. Variables, 2. Conditionals, 3. Functions, 4. Loops, 5. Lists
